{"id":265162,"type":1,"name":"少年ドールズ","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/57/f7/265162_MMzlR.jpg","summary":"扬羽平日是个平凡的高中女生，\r\n其实她是能够倾听人形声音的「人形师一族」。\r\n「人形师一族」皆拥有倾听人形声音的能力，并且解救灵魂受到污染的人形。\r\n「雷欧」和「雪」是人形师一族代代相传的特殊人形，\r\n透过人形师的亲吻，他们在夜里会变成人类的姿态。\r\n然而，扬羽的父母过世不久，「雪」也从此下落不明。\r\n扬羽因此和雷欧过着相依为命的生活。\r\n为了找回下落不明的「雪」，扬羽领着个性狂妄的雷欧展开了行动！","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>人形美少年</li><li><span>册数: </span>4</li><li><span>话数: </span>16+1</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/19200\">響ワタル</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/588\">白泉社</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span>月刊<a href=\"/person/9431\">LaLa</a>→<a href=\"/person/9431\">LaLa</a> DX、<a href=\"/person/9434\">LaLa DX</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>少年人偶</li><li><span>发售日: </span>2009-04-03</li><li><span>连载开始: </span>2009年</li><li><span>连载结束: </span>2011年9月号</li>","collection":{"wish":2,"collect":1,"on_hold":1},"tags":[{"name":"已完结","count":1},{"name":"少女","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":19200,"image":"","name":"响涉","desc":"作者"},{"id":588,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/2c/2a/588_prsn_0Fa4a.jpg","name":"白泉社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":9434,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/18/d8/9434_prsn_UZoO4.jpg","name":"LaLa DX","desc":"连载杂志"},{"id":9431,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/03/07/9431_prsn_cxvQO.jpg","name":"LaLa","desc":"连载杂志"}],"comic":[{"id":265163,"name":"少年ドールズ (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/ac/7c/265163_yC8ZT.jpg"},{"id":265164,"name":"少年ドールズ (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/e8/fd/265164_0700A.jpg"},{"id":265165,"name":"少年ドールズ (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/db/f6/265165_QxwjL.jpg"},{"id":265166,"name":"少年ドールズ (4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/fe/bd/265166_22Js0.jpg"}]}